{"type":"message","id":"fffec29e","parentId":"a571d8a6","timestamp":"2026-03-19T06:24:02.904Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户看到上传失败，错误是 500 (Internal Server Error)，前端尝试解析响应时收到 HTML 而不是 JSON。\n\n让我检查服务器日志中的错误。从之前的 log 输出中看到：\n```\nError: 不支持的音频格式\n    at fileFilter (C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\web-audio-player-server\\server.js:44:10)\n```\n\n所以错误是\"不支持的音频格式\"，服务器拒绝了上传。问题在于 multer 的 fileFilter 函数。\n\n让我检查 fileFilter 的实现：\n```javascript\nfileFilter: (req, file, cb) => {\n    const allowedTypes = /mp3|wav|ogg|flac|m4a/;\n    const extname = allowedTypes.test(path.extname(file.originalname).toLowerCase());\n    const mimetype = allowedTypes.test(file.mimetype);\n    if (extname && mimetype) {\n      cb(null, true);\n    } else {\n      cb(new Error('不支持的音频格式'));\n    }\n  }\n```\n\n问题在于这个正则表达式 `allowedTypes = /mp3|wav|ogg|flac|m4a/` 会匹配任何包含这些字符串的内容，但它 `.test()` 的结果会检查：\n- `extname` 是文件扩展名（如 `.mp3`）\n- `mimetype` 是 MIME 类型（如 `audio/mpeg`）\n\n`path.extname(file.originalname).toLowerCase()` 返回的是 `.mp3` 这样的字符串，而正则 `/mp3|wav|ogg|flac|m4a/` 匹配没问题，`.mp3` 包含 `mp3`。\n\n但是 `file.mimetype` 是 MIME 类型，比如 `audio/mpeg` 对于 MP3 文件，它不包含 `mp3` 这个字符串！所以 mimetype 测试会失败。\n\n对于 MP3，MIME 类型通常是 `audio/mpeg`，不是 `audio/mp3`。同理：\n- WAV: `audio/wav` 或 `audio/x-wav`\n- OGG: `audio/ogg`\n- FLAC: `audio/flac`\n- M4A: `audio/mp4` 或 `audio/x-m4a`\n\n所以这个 fileFilter 的 mimetype 检查太严格了，应该只检查扩展名，或者使用更宽松的 MIME 类型匹配。\n\n让我修改 fileFilter，只依赖扩展名检查，并允许常见的音频 MIME 类型。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"看到了！上传返回 500 错误，服务器日志显示\"不支持的音频格式\"。问题出在 `fileFilter` 的 MIME 类型检查太严格了。\n\n让我检查并修复这个问题："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b4fac90905b3438e9d6ecd5c","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\web-audio-player-server\\server.js","oldString":"  fileFilter: (req, file, cb) => {\n    const allowedTypes = /mp3|wav|ogg|flac|m4a/;\n    const extname = allowedTypes.test(path.extname(file.originalname).toLowerCase());\n    const mimetype = allowedTypes.test(file.mimetype);\n    if (extname && mimetype) {\n      cb(null, true);\n    } else {\n      cb(new Error('不支持的音频格式'));\n    }\n  }","newString":"  fileFilter: (req, file, cb) => {\n    const extname = path.extname(file.originalname).toLowerCase();\n    const allowedExtensions = ['.mp3', '.wav', '.ogg', '.flac', '.m4a'];\n    const allowedMimeTypes = [\n      'audio/mpeg',\n      'audio/mp3',\n      'audio/wav',\n      'audio/x-wav',\n      'audio/ogg',\n      'audio/flac',\n      'audio/mp4',\n      'audio/x-m4a',\n      'audio/mpeg4'\n    ];\n    \n    const isValidExtension = allowedExtensions.includes(extname);\n    const isValidMimeType = allowedMimeTypes.includes(file.mimetype);\n    \n    if (isValidExtension && isValidMimeType) {\n      cb(null, true);\n    } else {\n      cb(new Error('不支持的音频格式'));\n    }\n  }"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":42379,"output":1499,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43878,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773901430992}}
