{"type":"message","id":"a060f36d","parentId":"39d0f580","timestamp":"2026-03-19T10:04:42.113Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"工具 weather 不存在。让我查看可用的技能列表，看看有没有天气相关的工具。从可用技能列表中我看到有 \"weather\" 这个技能，描述是：\"Get current weather and forecasts (no API key required).\"\n\n让我尝试使用 weather 工具，但是也许需要的参数不同。让我重新检查可用技能列表，确实有 weather 这个技能。\n\n但是当我调用 weather 工具时，它说工具未找到。这可能是因为工具名称是 \"weather\" 而不是 \"weather\"。让我尝试正确的调用方式。在 OPENCLaw 中，工具名称是小的英文单词，我需要使用正确的工具名称。\n\n让我再检查一下工具列表。用户指南说技能提供工具，我需要找出正确的工具名称。在可用技能列表中，我看到：\n\n```\n<skill>\n  <name>weather</name>\n  <description>Get current weather and forecasts (no API key required).</description>\n  <location>...\\weather\\SKILL.md</location>\n</skill>\n```\n\n所以工具名称看起来是 \"weather\"。但我之前调用失败了。也许我需要检查是否有其他条件，比如是否需要安装这个技能。根据技能列表，这个技能应该已经安装了。\n\n让我再试一次调用 weather，这次使用正确的参数。也许 location 是必填的，我应该使用城市名。\n\n让我看看 SKILL.md 内容。我可以读取这个技能文件来了解正确的用法。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ee8608abe49e4ee4910a5222","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"E:\\agi\\opencode\\openclaw\\package\\skills\\weather\\SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":46323,"output":777,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47100,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773914671885}}
{"type":"message","id":"6d2b0873","parentId":"a060f36d","timestamp":"2026-03-19T10:04:42.195Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ee8608abe49e4ee4910a5222","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: weather\ndescription: \"Get current weather and forecasts via wttr.in or Open-Meteo. Use when: user asks about weather, temperature, or forecasts for any location. NOT for: historical weather data, severe weather alerts, or detailed meteorological analysis. No API key needed.\"\nhomepage: https://wttr.in/:help\nmetadata: { \"openclaw\": { \"emoji\": \"☔\", \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"curl\"] } } }\n---\n\n# Weather Skill\n\nGet current weather conditions and forecasts.\n\n## When to Use\n\n✅ **USE this skill when:**\n\n- \"What's the weather?\"\n- \"Will it rain today/tomorrow?\"\n- \"Temperature in [city]\"\n- \"Weather forecast for the week\"\n- Travel planning weather checks\n\n## When NOT to Use\n\n❌ **DON'T use this skill when:**\n\n- Historical weather data → use weather archives/APIs\n- Climate analysis or trends → use specialized data sources\n- Hyper-local microclimate data → use local sensors\n- Severe weather alerts → check official NWS sources\n- Aviation/marine weather → use specialized services (METAR, etc.)\n\n## Location\n\nAlways include a city, region, or airport code in weather queries.\n\n## Commands\n\n### Current Weather\n\n```bash\n# One-line summary\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?format=3\"\n\n# Detailed current conditions\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?0\"\n\n# Specific city\ncurl \"wttr.in/New+York?format=3\"\n```\n\n### Forecasts\n\n```bash\n# 3-day forecast\ncurl \"wttr.in/London\"\n\n# Week forecast\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?format=v2\"\n\n# Specific day (0=today, 1=tomorrow, 2=day after)\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?1\"\n```\n\n### Format Options\n\n```bash\n# One-liner\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?format=%l:+%c+%t+%w\"\n\n# JSON output\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?format=j1\"\n\n# PNG image\ncurl \"wttr.in/London.png\"\n```\n\n### Format Codes\n\n- `%c` — Weather condition emoji\n- `%t` — Temperature\n- `%f` — \"Feels like\"\n- `%w` — Wind\n- `%h` — Humidity\n- `%p` — Precipitation\n- `%l` — Location\n\n## Quick Responses\n\n**\"What's the weather?\"**\n\n```bash\ncurl -s \"wttr.in/London?format=%l:+%c+%t+(feels+like+%f),+%w+wind,+%h+humidity\"\n```\n\n**\"Will it rain?\"**\n\n```bash\ncurl -s \"wttr.in/London?format=%l:+%c+%p\"\n```\n\n**\"Weekend forecast\"**\n\n```bash\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?format=v2\"\n```\n\n## Notes\n\n- No API key needed (uses wttr.in)\n- Rate limited; don't spam requests\n- Works for most global cities\n- Supports airport codes: `curl wttr.in/ORD`\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773914682191}}
