{"type":"message","id":"57055523","parentId":"dd1e5898","timestamp":"2026-03-19T12:42:50.712Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-6331a60851044f969bbe385efd205b24","toolName":"browser","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"browser\",\n  \"error\": \"timed out. Restart the OpenClaw gateway (OpenClaw.app menubar, or `openclaw gateway`). Do NOT retry the browser tool — it will keep failing. Use an alternative approach or inform the user that the browser is currently unavailable.\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"browser","error":"timed out. Restart the OpenClaw gateway (OpenClaw.app menubar, or `openclaw gateway`). Do NOT retry the browser tool — it will keep failing. Use an alternative approach or inform the user that the browser is currently unavailable."},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773924170710}}
{"type":"message","id":"c9dd41c1","parentId":"57055523","timestamp":"2026-03-19T12:42:58.251Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"浏览器超时了。让我直接用 PowerShell 打开默认浏览器访问官网，或者尝试找到直接的下载链接。\n\n我可以使用 `Start-Process` 或 `Invoke-Item` 来打开网页。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"浏览器超时了。让我直接打开官网下载页面："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-02a30434fcca4c24b2aaf00cf85742fe","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"start https://qclaw.qq.com/"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773924170714}}
{"type":"message","id":"e02aad5c","parentId":"c9dd41c1","timestamp":"2026-03-19T12:42:59.881Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-02a30434fcca4c24b2aaf00cf85742fe","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"(no output)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1622,"aggregated":"","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773924179878}}
{"type":"message","id":"8da470e3","parentId":"e02aad5c","timestamp":"2026-03-19T12:43:11.273Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我已经打开了 QClaw 官网。现在用户应该能在浏览器中看到下载页面了。让我总结一下 QClaw 的信息和下载步骤。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **已打开 QClaw 官网！**\n\n---\n\n## 🦞 **QClaw 介绍**\n\n**QClaw** 是腾讯电脑管家团队推出的**本地 AI 智能体助手**，基于 OpenClaw 开源框架封装：\n\n### 核心功能：\n- 📱 **微信直联**：扫码绑定微信，直接在微信中发送指令远程操控电脑\n- 💻 **QQ 集成**：支持 QQ 远程操控\n- 🎯 **自动部署**：支持 Mac & Windows，一键安装即用\n- 🧠 **内置国产大模型**：Kimi、Minimax、GLM、DeepSeek 等\n- 🦞 **持续记忆**：记住偏好和上下文，越养越聪明\n- 🔧 **Skills 生态**：支持 ClawHub、GitHub 等丰富生态\n\n### 使用步骤：\n1. 📥 点击官网「立即下载」按钮\n2. 🖥️ 运行安装包，一键安装\n3. 📱 打开 QClaw，扫码绑定微信\n4. 🚀 开始使用！\n\n---\n\n**请在刚打开的浏览器页面中点击「立即下载」按钮下载安装。** 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773924179883}}
{"type":"message","id":"bac81f5a","parentId":"8da470e3","timestamp":"2026-03-19T12:44:56.505Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-03-19 20:44 GMT+8] 你来安装啊，别老是让主人干活啊"}],"timestamp":1773924296501}}
{"type":"message","id":"8f4180b1","parentId":"bac81f5a","timestamp":"2026-03-19T12:45:13.932Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户希望我直接帮他下载安装 QClaw，而不是让他自己去操作。他说\"别老是让主人干活啊\"，说明他希望我更主动地完成任务。\n\n让我尝试直接下载 QClaw 的安装包。根据之前搜索到的信息：\n- 官网是 https://qclaw.qq.com/\n- 有 Windows 和 Mac 版本\n\n我需要找到下载链接，然后下载安装包。让我先分析一下网页内容，找到下载链接。\n\n由于浏览器超时，我需要用其他方式获取下载链接。让我直接尝试下载 Windows 版本的安装包。\n\n根据搜索结果，可能的下载链接格式：\n- https://qclaw.qq.com/download/windows\n- https://qclaw.qq.com/download\n- 或者是某个 CDN 链接\n\n让我尝试用 PowerShell 直接下载。首先需要获取实际的下载链接。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的主人！让我直接帮你下载安装 QClaw！"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-8e98ea855b4f410994980f2e252c9018","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"powershell -Command \"$response = Invoke-WebRequest -Uri 'https://qclaw.qq.com/' -UseBasicParsing; $response.Content\" 2>&1 | head -100"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773924296504}}
