{"type":"message","id":"d1f05405","parentId":"d8b24a01","timestamp":"2026-03-19T13:43:24.766Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想把默认大模型换成 bailian 的 Kimi 2.5。我需要使用 session_status 工具来设置模型覆盖，或者使用 gateway 的 config.patch 来修改配置。\n\n让我查看一下如何修改默认模型。根据工具描述，session_status 可以设置 per-session model override：\n\"Show a /status-equivalent session status card (usage + time + cost when available). Use for model-use questions (📊 session_status); optional per-session model override (model=default resets overrides).\"\n\n参数是 `model` 可以设置模型。\n\n但这是 per-session 的覆盖，不是永久的默认模型。要永久修改，需要使用 gateway 的 config.patch 或 config.apply。\n\n让我先查看当前的模型配置结构，使用 config.schema.lookup 来查看模型配置的路径。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！让我帮你把默认模型换成 Bailian 的 Kimi 2.5。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-fb393b900e2f4f4781e95c41e7451105","name":"gateway","arguments":{"action":"config.schema.lookup","gatewayToken":"default"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773927793969}}
