{"type":"message","id":"1b5c5b3a","parentId":"8d9c4723","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:30:55.373Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我已经把任务配置备份到了 MEMORY.md。现在我需要告诉用户：\n\n1. 已经把任务配置备份到 MEMORY.md\n2. 需要备份的关键文件列表\n3. 下次恢复时的流程\n\n让我整理一个完整的备份指南给用户。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **已解决！** 我做了两件事：\n\n---\n\n## 📦 **备份方案**\n\n### 1. 任务配置已写入我的记忆（MEMORY.md）\n即使 GitHub 恢复时丢失任务文件，我也能从记忆中恢复！\n\n### 2. 需要备份到 GitHub 的关键文件：\n\n| 文件 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` | 主配置（模型、频道、插件等） |\n| `~/.openclaw/cron/jobs.json` | **定时任务配置** ⚠️ |\n| `~/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md` | 我的长期记忆 |\n| `~/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md` | 心跳任务配置 |\n| `~/.openclaw/workspace/AGENTS.md` | 工作原则 |\n\n---\n\n## 🔄 **下次恢复流程**\n\n1. **从 GitHub 恢复文件到 `~/.openclaw/`**\n2. **重启网关：** `openclaw gateway restart`\n3. **任务自动恢复** ✅（如果 `cron/jobs.json` 存在）\n\n**如果任务丢失：**\n- 查看 MEMORY.md 中的任务配置\n- 用命令手动恢复\n\n---\n\n现在你的任务已经双重备份了：\n- ✅ 文件备份：`~/.openclaw/cron/jobs.json`\n- ✅ 记忆备份：`MEMORY.md`\n\n下次恢复 GitHub 时，记得把 `cron/jobs.json` 也一起恢复！🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773934238330}}
